\v 50 eŐĀ walii zoni, eŐĀ …†ula Izilay…õle nuiti ti-loun zunu m…Ēungiti zea, eŐĀ …†…õ ga wali …†ae waagila unsa ča puul…Ēzita maazu l…Ē…Ēlug…Ē (1.365), e…†…õ čelei seizu …≤adegai ma walii la.  
