\v 30 ¬ęK…õl…õ nu-o-nu, nii a gaa…†ili ma, eŐĀ kotoi …†…õ, Izilay…õle nui, eŐĀ ga zou loin, …ďaa seik…Ē…†…Ēma nui, eŐĀ ∆ď…Ēo…†…Ē GALAGI l…Ē…†…Ēi …†olo…†ologa, kpe ka le če naŐĀ-nu…ďus…õiti ba, eŐĀ …†ula ti zaama.  
\v 31 EŐĀ ∆ď…Ēo…†…Ē GALAGI laawooi  č…õl…õ čiliga, eŐĀ naŐĀ-deveiti kolo…†olo, k…õni kpe ge le če naŐĀ-nuiti ba. NaŐĀ-faa…†aaza golai ma …†as…Ēi …†a la unma.¬Ľ 
